prompt: Photorealistic educational display illustrating the concept of value in art. The sphere clearly shows a full range of values from bright highlight to deep core shadow. Minimalist composition, clean studio lighting, sharp focus, high detail. Professional informative imagery. Professional photography style, intimate mood. Wide landscape composition, 16:9 aspect ratio.
